<P>
   WINE-LABELS (San Francisco) _ Continuing his all-out assault on
the wine industry, Sen. Strom Thurmond, R-S.C., said he believes
San Francisco's Wine Institute and senior government officials may
have conspired to manipulate government nutritional guidelines to
promote the sale of alcohol. By LARRY D. HATFIELD.
