<P>
   SAILOR-SHIP (Boston) _ A former seaman apprentice and the
retired warship USS Massachusetts -- thrown together by fate for
the battleship's maiden voyage -- to reunite after the ship's
refurbishing is complete. By Thomas Farragher. 770 words. PHOTO
</P>
<P>
   &UR; COMMENTARY (k) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   MCGRORY-COLUMN (Undated) _ Let's begin with a proclamation
that's a firing offense in 1999 America: Blacks and Hispanics are
