<HEADLINE>
ALL ABOUT DECORATING TIPS 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   PHOENIX -
</P>
<P>
   - Round tips 2, 4 and 7 for outlines, printing, dots, vines,
cornelli lace. &QL; 
- Open star tips 13, 16, 17, 18 and 199 for multipoint stars,
shells, drop flowers. &QL; 
- Closed star tip 30 for deeply carved decorations. &QL; 
- Multiopening tip 42 for double rows of lines, beads, dots and
scallops. &QL; 
- Ribbon or basketweave tips 46 and 47 for smooth or ribbed
stripes, basketweave. &QL; 
- Petal tips 97, 101, 102, 103 and 104 for lifelike petaled
flowers, ruffles, swags and drapes. &QL; 
- Specialty tips 78 and 98 for unique stars and shells, 61 for
roses and 74 for poinsettias. &QL; 
- Drop flower tips 106 and 107 for plain or swirled blooms. &QL; 
- For leaves, 65, 66 and 67. &QL;
</P>
