   COMMENTARY (``k'' category)
</P>
<P>
   MEANS-COLUMN (Washington) _ The craze for term limits is fading
as House Republican incumbents who embraced the concept stall about
meeting their deadlines and actually carrying out their pledges to
leave Congress. By MARIANNE MEANS.
</P>
