await in crystal-blue Banff, Alberta. (INCLUDES TWO COLOR
PHOTOGRAPHS OF POPULAR SITES IN BANFF)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: TRAVEL TIPS: Things to do when traveling to Banff.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: DESTINATIONS: If you can't decide which ports of call to
make, choose the world. A world cruise is not only possible, but
becoming affordable.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: TRAVEL BRIEFS: The new National Center for Popular Music
has opened in Sheffield in northern England. The center was created
to inform visitors about the history and impact of pop music.
