   &UR; ENTERTAINMENT &LR;  (``e'' code)
</P>
<P>
   KING-LEAR (Undated) _ A Critic's Notebook: Listening to ``King
Lear,'' then reading the play. By Christopher Lehmann-Haupt.
</P>
<P>
   DANCE-TECH (Tempe, Ariz.) _ The International Dance and
Technology Conference is held in Tempe, Ariz. By Jennifer Dunning.
</P>
