<HEADLINE>
&HT;    
 &HT;    
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    HEISMAN WINNER TACKLES READING PROGRAM
 &HT;    with photos
 &HT;    moving in (w) Washington and (s) Sports categories
