<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    SAFETY ADVOCATES WANT TIGHTER TRUCKING REGULATION
 &HT;    With TRUCK-SAFETY. For release Sunday, March 7.
 &HT;    By BOB DART
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
