<P>
   DONT-TALK - Talk, talk and talk some more. That's the advice
relationship ``experts'' have long given couples with problems.
Well, forget it. A long-term study by two universities found that
couples with great communications skills aren't necessarily any
happier. The smart communicators simply insulted each other more
effectively. (Reed, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
