   BASKETBALL
</P>
<P>
   BKC-ACC-DUKE _ The 46th annual ACC Men's Basketball Tournament,
which some are calling the Duke Coronation, begins Thursday at the
Charlotte Coliseum. Can anybody beat the No. 1 Blue Devils? Not if
they are hitting on all cylinders, say basketball experts. Some are
even saying that this is the best Duke team Mike Krzyzewski has
fielded in Durham. He would like to win this tournament but not at
the expense of getting his team ready for the NCAA Tournament,
where the Blue Devils are expected to be the No. 1 seed (Barnhart)
18-20.
