television and film a year ago organized the Morning Star
Commission under the auspices of Hadassah to work toward changing
Jewish women's stereotypical image on Televison. By Joseph Hanania.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ANTIQUES &LR;
</P>
<P>
   KIASMA-ARCH-ANTIQUES (Helsinki, Finland) _ At a time when much
new architecture is almost interchangeable from country to country,
the Kiasma Museum in Helsinki is distinctive for the way it
expresses the national character of Finland and its landscape. The
name itself describes an intertwining of genetic material, but here
it takes on a more metaphoric meaning, evoking the confluence of
the urban streets that surround the museum. By Paula Deitz.
</P>
