   (NYT5) ORLANDO, Fla. -- March 02, 1999 -- EPCOT-SPEEDWAY-NYTR-1,
3-02 -- Visitors to Test Track, a new attraction at Disney World,
race past at 65 mph on a banked turn at Epcot Center in Orlando.
Though it doesn't officially open until March 17, the ride is
